results.name: A bisection of A000957.
formula: Conjecture: D-finite with recurrence 4*n*(2*n-1)*(7*n-13)*a(n) +(-910*n^3+3489*n^2-4277*n+1680)*a(n-1) +2*(4*n-7)*(7*n-6)*(4*n-5)*a(n-2)=0. Telescoping would provide another recurrence for A000957. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 26 2020
